OL,3,CWhy Labour thinks the Conservatives
OL,4,Cand Reform have got it wrong on Iran
OL,6,FLabour MPs, fresh from a weekend back
OL,7,Fin their constituencies, have returned
OL,8,Fto Westminster with two broad concerns
OL,9,Fabout the war in Iran: one is that a
OL,10,Fhuge economic shock is about to hit
OL,11,Fthe UK and - similar to the shock felt
OL,12,Fafter Russia's invasion of Ukraine -
OL,13,Fit could be felt for years to come.
OL,15,FThe second concern is that Europe
OL,16,Fcould face a massive refugee crisis on
OL,17,Fa scale not seen since the war in
OL,18,FSyria.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
