OL,3,CWhy Labour thinks the Conservatives
OL,4,Cand Reform have got it wrong on Iran
OL,6,FThen, millions of refugees travelled
OL,7,Fto Europe, with many eventually
OL,8,Fsettling in Germany. This time, MPs
OL,9,Fbelieve millions of Iranians - many of
OL,10,Fwhom have family ties to the UK - will
OL,11,Fseek asylum here in Britain.
OL,13,FPublic opinion is firmly against the
OL,14,FUK getting more involved in the
OL,15,Fconflict - just eight percent of
OL,16,Fvoters in a recent YouGov survey said
OL,17,Fthe UK military should join US and
OL,18,FIsraeli airstrikes against Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
