OL,3,CWhy Labour thinks the Conservatives
OL,4,Cand Reform have got it wrong on Iran
OL,6,FLabour believes its current response
OL,7,Fis broadly in line with public
OL,8,Fopinion. And the party is now seeking
OL,9,Fto call out its opponents on the right.
OL,11,FSenior Labour figures have been
OL,12,Fhighlighting what they see as an
OL,13,Finconsistent response from Reform UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
