OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773173478
OL,3,CWhy Labour thinks the Conservatives
OL,4,Cand Reform have got it wrong on Iran
OL,6,FThey point to comments from Nigel
OL,7,FFarage - who has gone from saying "the
OL,8,Fgloves need to come off" and the UK
OL,9,F"should do all we can to support the
OL,10,Foperation" led by the US and Israel -
OL,11,Fto today arguing that the UK should
OL,12,Fnot "get involved in another foreign
OL,13,Fwar."
OL,15,F"If he had been Prime Minister he
OL,16,Fwould have already dragged our country
OL,17,Finto this war and wouldn't be able to
OL,18,Fu-turn like he has done today," said
OL,19,Fthe Chair of the Labour Party, Anna
OL,20,FTurley.
