OL,3,CWhy Labour thinks the Conservatives
OL,4,Cand Reform have got it wrong on Iran
OL,6,FLabour have also pointed out the
OL,7,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch has
OL,8,Fbeen far more supportive of the US
OL,9,Fdecision to bomb Iran.
OL,11,FEven public criticism from President
OL,12,FTrump - in which the US president said
OL,13,Fof Keir Starmer "this is not Winston
OL,14,FChurchill we're dealing with" - hasn't
OL,15,Foverly worried the prime ministers
OL,16,Faides. They are fairly relaxed about
OL,17,FKeir Starmer being seen to stand up to
OL,18,Fa US president who is deeply unpopular
OL,19,Fwith the British public.
OL,26,@uD@QOUvD@]O]
