OL,3,CWhy Labour thinks the Conservatives
OL,4,Cand Reform have got it wrong on Iran
OL,6,FAlmost twenty five years on from the
OL,7,Fwar in Iraq, politicians on both sides
OL,8,Fof the Atlantic are still asked about
OL,9,Fwhether they supported the US-led
OL,10,Finvasion in 2003.
OL,12,FIf the conflict in Iran goes on for
OL,13,Fanywhere near as long as the war in
OL,14,FIraq - and its consequences for the
OL,15,Fmiddle east and wider world are
OL,16,Fanywhere near as destabilising -
OL,17,FBritish politicians will be held to
OL,18,Fwhat they say now for years to come.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
